
@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Privacy_Policy";
    Layout = null;
}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Privacy Policy - Remote Sensing</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }

        .policy-container {
            background: #fff;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }

        h1, h2 {
            font-weight: 700;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container py-5">
        <div class="policy-container">
            <h1 class="mb-3">Privacy Policy</h1>
            <p><strong>Last Updated:</strong> 10 December 2025</p>

            <p>
                Remote Sensing (“the App”) is committed to protecting your privacy.
                This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our mobile application.
            </p>

            <hr>

            <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>

            <h5>a. Personal Information</h5>
            <p>We may collect basic user information such as:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Name</li>
                <li>Email address</li>
                <li>Mobile number</li>
                <li>User role (Admin, Project Manager, Subordinate, Outsource, Accounts)</li>
            </ul>

            <h5>b. Project & Usage Data</h5>
            <p>To support project management features, the App may collect:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Project details</li>
                <li>Task updates</li>
                <li>Meeting schedules</li>
                <li>Tour proposals</li>
                <li>Reimbursement and fund requests</li>
                <li>Activity logs</li>
            </ul>

            <h5>c. Device & Technical Information</h5>
            <ul>
                <li>Device type</li>
                <li>Operating system</li>
                <li>App version</li>
                <li>Log data</li>
            </ul>

            <hr>

            <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <p>We use collected information to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Provide and maintain app features</li>
                <li>Enable user login and role-based access</li>
                <li>Facilitate project creation, workflow management, and approvals</li>
                <li>Improve app performance and user experience</li>
                <li>Communicate important updates or support messages</li>
                <li>Ensure data security and prevent unauthorized access</li>
            </ul>

            <hr>

            <h2>3. Data Sharing & Disclosure</h2>
            <p>We do not sell or share your personal data with third parties for marketing purposes.</p>

            <hr>

            <h2>4. Data Storage & Security</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>End-to-end encryption for stored data</li>
                <li>Secure login and role-based access controls</li>
                <li>Firewalls and intrusion monitoring</li>
            </ul>
            <p>All data is stored securely on device or protected cloud servers (if applicable).</p>

            <hr>

            <h2>5. User Rights</h2>
            <p>You may request to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Access your personal data</li>
                <li>Correct inaccurate information</li>
                <li>Delete your account or data (subject to organisational rules)</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Contact us using the information below for any such requests.</p>

            <hr>

            <h2>6. Children’s Privacy</h2>
            <p>
                The App is not intended for children under the age of 13.
                We do not knowingly collect data from children.
            </p>

            <hr>

            <h2>7. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
            <p>
                We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time.
                Any changes will be reflected on this page with an updated revision date.
            </p>

           
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>

</body>
</html>


